info.title: GIPS API
info.description: Allow clients to use GIPS through APIs.

post.description:
This endpoint runs the GIPS calculation specified in the POST body parameters.
It can take upto 2 units.

Remarks:

*	Any settings in POST body will act as a one-time override over the settings saved in the GIPS template.
Use this endpoint to trigger calculation requests.

parameters.name: X-FactSet-Api-Long-Running-Deadline
parameters.description: The number of seconds the request will wait before sending back the response. If not provided, 20 will be used as default.

requestBody.description: The request body contains the information needed to run a calculation, e.g. the GIPS composite. See the schema for more details.
